    %% RHODS Operator Dependencies (Platform Core)
    RHODS -->|deploys & manages| Gateway
    RHODS -->|deploys & manages| AuthProxy
    RHODS -->|deploys & manages| Dashboard
    RHODS -->|deploys & manages| NotebookCtrl
    RHODS -->|deploys & manages| DSPOp
