    RHODS -->|requires| GatewayAPI
    RHODS -->|requires| OAuth
    RHODS -->|requires| ContainerRegistry

    %% Gateway Infrastructure Dependencies
    Gateway -->|requires| GatewayAPI
    Gateway -->|integrates| Istio
    AuthProxy -->|authenticates via| OAuth

    %% Dashboard Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|manages via API| NotebookCtrl
    Dashboard -->|manages via API| DSPOp
    Dashboard -->|manages via API| KServe
    Dashboard -->|manages via API| ModelRegOp
    Dashboard -->|manages via API| FeastOp
    Dashboard -->|manages via API| LlamaStackOp
    Dashboard -->|queries| K8sAPI

    %% Notebook Controller Dependencies
    NotebookCtrl -->|creates| K8sAPI
    NotebookCtrl -.->|optional| Istio

    %% DSP Operator Dependencies
    DSPOp -->|deploys to| KServe
    DSPOp -->|registers to| ModelRegOp
    DSPOp -->|stores artifacts| S3
    DSPOp -->|persists metadata| ExternalDB
    DSPOp -->|creates workflows| K8sAPI

    %% KServe Dependencies
    KServe -.->|serverless mode| Knative
    KServe -.->|serverless mode| Istio
    KServe -->|downloads models| S3
    KServe -.->|queries metadata| ModelRegOp
    KServe -.->|queries features| FeastOp
    KServe -->|downloads models| HuggingFace
    KServe -->|creates services| K8sAPI

    %% ODH Model Controller Dependencies
    ModelCtrl -->|extends| KServe
    ModelCtrl -->|queries| NvidiaNCG
    ModelCtrl -->|creates Routes/ServiceMonitors| K8sAPI

    %% Model Registry Operator Dependencies
    ModelRegOp -->|stores metadata| ExternalDB
    ModelRegOp -->|creates services| K8sAPI

    %% Training Operator Dependencies
    TrainingOp -->|registers models| ModelRegOp
    TrainingOp -->|stores checkpoints| S3
    TrainingOp -->|creates training jobs| K8sAPI

    %% KubeRay Operator Dependencies
    KubeRayOp -->|loads data| S3
    KubeRayOp -->|creates clusters| K8sAPI
    KubeRayOp -.->|optional certs| CertManager

    %% TrustyAI Operator Dependencies
    TrustyAIOp -->|monitors| KServe
    TrustyAIOp -->|stores data| S3
    TrustyAIOp -.->|persists data| ExternalDB
    TrustyAIOp -->|creates services| K8sAPI

    %% Feast Operator Dependencies
    FeastOp -->|stores features| S3
    FeastOp -->|stores registry| ExternalDB
    FeastOp -->|creates services| K8sAPI

    %% Llama Stack Operator Dependencies
    LlamaStackOp -->|downloads models| HuggingFace
    LlamaStackOp -->|creates deployments| K8sAPI

    %% Monitoring Dependencies
    Prometheus -->|scrapes metrics| Dashboard
    Prometheus -->|scrapes metrics| NotebookCtrl
    Prometheus -->|scrapes metrics| DSPOp
    Prometheus -->|scrapes metrics| KServe
    Prometheus -->|scrapes metrics| ModelCtrl
    Prometheus -->|scrapes metrics| ModelRegOp
    Prometheus -->|scrapes metrics| TrainingOp
    Prometheus -->|scrapes metrics| KubeRayOp
    Prometheus -->|scrapes metrics| TrustyAIOp
    Prometheus -->|scrapes metrics| FeastOp
    Prometheus -->|scrapes metrics| LlamaStackOp

